ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce du grand Châteauguay ** Change Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DU GRAND CHÂTEAUGUAY, in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of its district from Châteauguay, Léry, Mercier, Saint-Isidore-de-la-Prairie, Sainte Martine and Saint-Urbain-Premier to Châteauguay, Léry, Mercier, Saint Isidore de-la-Prairie, Sainte-Martine, Saint-Urbain-Premier, La Prairie, Candiac, Saint-Philippe, Saint-Mathieu, Delson, Saint-Constant, Sainte-Catherine, Saint-Rémi, Saint-Michel, Saint-Édouard, Sainte-Clothilde, St-Patrice-de-Sherrington and Hemmingford.
